  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899300/extras/bfedcefc7c61da0f283482b8e3e74fa7.poster.avif?t=1773606734\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899300/extras/bfedcefc7c61da0f283482b8e3e74fa7.webm?t=1773606734\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><strong>Combat Complex</strong> is a fast-paced ARPG / roguelike hybrid with lasers, alien bugs, WASD / twin-stick controls, random loot, and procedurally-generated levels. Wield legendary weapons, unlock devastating skills, create overpowered builds – and turn your enemies' attacks against them. Try the free demo!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ARPG / ROGUELIKE HYBRID</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Loot is permanent (as soon as you bring it home) but power-ups are lost on death.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >TURN YOUR ENEMIES' ATTACKS AGAINST THEM!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lure them into their own lasers, or pull them into their own exploding bombs. Get creative! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PROCEDURALLY-GENERATED LEVELS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No level is the same – levels are generated procedurally to keep the challenge fresh. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >RANDOM LOOT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rare, epic, and legendary random loot – railguns, pulse rifles, flamethrowers and more! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HORDES OF ENEMIES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This won't be easy. Prepare to get overwhelmed. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SKILL IS EVERYTHING</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's not just about your stats. You'll need lightning-fast reflexes and quick thinking to survive. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >STATS AND SKILL TREE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become a hard-to-kill tank, a deadly glass cannon, or a space wizard!  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SINGLE-PLAYER ONLY (SO FAR)</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is currently single-player only, though we may add multiplayer later. </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899300/extras/bfedcefc7c61da0f283482b8e3e74fa7.poster.avif?t=1773606734\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899300/extras/bfedcefc7c61da0f283482b8e3e74fa7.webm?t=1773606734\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><strong>Combat Complex</strong> is a fast-paced ARPG / roguelike hybrid with lasers, alien bugs, WASD / twin-stick controls, random loot, and procedurally-generated levels. Wield legendary weapons, unlock devastating skills, create overpowered builds – and turn your enemies' attacks against them. Try the free demo!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ARPG / ROGUELIKE HYBRID</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Loot is permanent (as soon as you bring it home) but power-ups are lost on death.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >TURN YOUR ENEMIES' ATTACKS AGAINST THEM!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lure them into their own lasers, or pull them into their own exploding bombs. Get creative! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PROCEDURALLY-GENERATED LEVELS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No level is the same – levels are generated procedurally to keep the challenge fresh. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >RANDOM LOOT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rare, epic, and legendary random loot – railguns, pulse rifles, flamethrowers and more! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HORDES OF ENEMIES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This won't be easy. Prepare to get overwhelmed. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SKILL IS EVERYTHING</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's not just about your stats. You'll need lightning-fast reflexes and quick thinking to survive. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >STATS AND SKILL TREE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become a hard-to-kill tank, a deadly glass cannon, or a space wizard!  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SINGLE-PLAYER ONLY (SO FAR)</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is currently single-player only, though we may add multiplayer later. </p>",
